Class ReportsController

java.lang.Object
Controllers.ReportsController
public class ReportsController extends Object
This class is the controller for the Reports screen. It handles the logic for the reports screen. It also contains LAMBDA EXPRESSION #2 ----LAMBDA EXPRESSION #2---- A lambda expression is used to set the cell values in a few columns. I was unable to get the columns to populate with the correct data using PropertyValueFactory. I was able to get the data to populate using Lambda expressions.
